acme.validation.ticker.message		= The ticker must have exactly two capital letters and two digits, a dash, and between five or ten numbers, letters or underscores. Example: AB12-EX_Tick12
acme.validation.text.message   		= Must have from 1 to 255 characters
acme.validation.header.message  	= Must have from 1 to 75 characters

acme.validation.strategy.no-tactics-and-published.message = If the strategy is published, it must have at least one tactic associated
acme.validation.strategy.correct-interval.message = If the strategy is published, the start moment must be before the end moment
acme.validation.strategy.duplicated-ticker.message = There is already a strategy with the given ticker